data.message:
**Welcome to the GolmiEval Task!** Describe the highlighted piece on the board on the 
right so that another person could **uniquely** identify it. 
When in doubt, click on a piece to find out if that's your target.
Here's a little help: you can reference pieces according to this legend
The rightmost teal N piece at the bottom of the bord
**You need to send at least one message before you can move on.** Remember to press enter to send your description
The olive green L piece in the left upper corner.
**You need to send at least one message before you can move on.** Remember to press enter to send your description
The teal X-shaped piece on the left in the middle of two other teal X pieces.
The olive-green L piece.
The olive-green W piece.
Still 10 boards to go
The leftmost V-shaped red piece which just about touches another red V piece.
**You need to send at least one message before you can move on.** Remember to press enter to send your description
The olive-green L piece right on top of the brown T
The grey I piece in the left bottom corner.
The topmost blue X-shaped piece.
The lower one of the pair of brown Y pieces in the center upper part of the board.
Still 5 boards to go. You almost made it!
**You need to send at least one message before you can move on.** Remember to press enter to send your description
The topmost orange L shaped piece on the board.
The grey W piece.
The dark blue I piece and the touching royal blue N piece in the center-left lower part of the board.
The brown Z piece in the center of the board touching the blue U piece.
The pink F piece on the top
That was the last one 🎉 🎉 thank you very much for your time! I really appreciate your help.
The room is closing, see you next time 👋
